        {
            "description": "Plucked: extended Karplus-Strong string. A one-period noise burst (bandwidth = pick hardness) is comb-filtered by pick position, then circulates in a fractional-delay loop with a one-zero damping filter and a 3-stage allpass dispersion chain. Loop gain is derived from t60, so decay time is a physical parameter, not a magic number."
